APPROVED b6a6e4921b436b8983ce148594ac393ee2de1b57
Users can now run `cw doctor` to get a pass/fail readiness check (Node version, agent backend, git, writable state) before starting a workflow, and corrupt authoritative state files now surface explicit errors instead of silently returning wrong data.

